  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个流程图，展示患者从社区到住院的整个路径，重点是要突出access block机制——就是出院受阻导致床位占满、反过来影响急诊的那个反馈循环。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Community",
        "ED_Arrival",
        "Inpatient",
        "access block mechanism"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，起点是Community，然后分两条路：一条是经GP到急诊，另一条是直接ED arrival？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Community",
        "GP",
        "ED_Arrival"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，GP和直接到急诊这两种入口都要保留。GP那边标注成\"GP / primary care\"，用蓝色系表示社区医疗环节。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "GP",
        "primary care"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，Community节点用中性灰色，GP用浅蓝色填充。接下来ED arrival之后是什么？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Community",
        "GP",
        "ED_Arrival"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "ED arrival之后是ED assessment & treatment，这是关键状态节点，用红色系突出。然后到Decision to admit，这里要中性色，表示决策点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ED_Arrival",
        "ED_Treat",
        "Admission"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "ED_Treat用浅红填充，Admission用灰色。Decision to admit之后就是Inpatient stay？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Admission",
        "Inpatient"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "没错，Inpatient stay也是状态节点，同样红色系。然后到Ready for discharge，这里开始出现blockages。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Inpatient",
        "Ready",
        "blockages"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "blockages具体指什么？是两种约束条件吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "constraints",
        "blockages"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，一种是Aged care placement，养老机构床位不足；另一种是NDIS supports / accommodation，残障人士住宿安排延迟或错配。这两个都是capacity constraint。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Block_Aged",
        "Block_NDIS",
        "aged",
        "ndis",
        "accommodati"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "这两个block节点我用橙色虚线边框，加上risk的样式定义。它们从Ready for discharge分出来？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Ready",
        "Block_Aged",
        "Block_NDIS",
        "risk",
        "dasharray"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Ready同时指向这两个block。现在最关键的部分：occupancy feedback loop——Block_Aged要有一条虚线连回Inpatient，表示因为出不去所以继续占床。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Block_Aged",
        "Inpatient",
        "feedback",
        "occupancy feedback loop"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "虚线连接Block_Aged到Inpatient，标注\"occupancy feedback loop\"。那Block_NDIS也需要这条反馈线吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Block_NDIS",
        "Inpatient",
        "feedback"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "Block_NDIS主要是逻辑上的约束，但反馈机制的核心体现用Block_Aged那条就够了。不过可以加上另一条虚线：Inpatient连回ED_Treat，标注high occupancy limits flow，显示床位满了之后急诊也受影响。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Inpatient",
        "ED_Treat",
        "high occupancy limits flow"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "所以有两条反馈虚线：一条是Block_Aged到Inpatient的occupancy loop，另一条是Inpatient到ED_Treat的flow limit。对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Block_Aged",
